searchQuery.query:
source logs 
| filter $l.subsystemname == 'cx_rum'
| filter cx_rum.session_context.user_email != null
| redact $d.cx_rum.session_context.user_email matching /@.*/ to '@xxxxxxxx.com'
| countby $d.cx_rum.session_context.browser, $d.cx_rum.session_context.user_email, $d.cx_rum.network_request_context.url, $d.cx_rum.network_request_context.status_code
| filter cx_rum.network_request_context.status_code:num > 399
| orderby _count desc
